column16: Wade Miley grounds into a double play, shortstop Clint Barmes to second baseman John McDonald to first baseman Gaby Sanchez.   Josh Wilson out at 2nd.
Josh Wilson grounds into a force out, third baseman Josh Harrison to second baseman John McDonald.   Alfredo Marte to 3rd.    Cliff Pennington out at 2nd.    Josh Wilson to 1st.
Cliff Pennington singles on a ground ball to right fielder Jose Tabata.   Alfredo Marte to 2nd.
Alfredo Marte singles on a soft line drive to left fielder Travis Snider.
Miguel Montero grounds out sharply, second baseman John McDonald to first baseman Gaby Sanchez.
Martin Prado grounds out, shortstop Clint Barmes to first baseman Gaby Sanchez.
A.  J.   Pollock called out on strikes.
Wade Miley grounds out, shortstop Clint Barmes to first baseman Gaby Sanchez.   Alfredo Marte scores.    Cliff Pennington to 3rd.    Josh Wilson to 2nd.
Josh Wilson walks.   Miguel Montero scores.    Alfredo Marte to 3rd.    Cliff Pennington to 2nd.
Cliff Pennington walks.   Paul Goldschmidt scores.    Miguel Montero to 3rd.    Alfredo Marte to 2nd.
Alfredo Marte walks.   Paul Goldschmidt to 3rd.    Miguel Montero to 2nd.
Ramon Hernandez called out on strikes.
Jerry Hairston grounds into a force out, shortstop Clint Barmes to second baseman Neil Walker.   Adrian Gonzalez out at 2nd.
Adrian Gonzalez singles on a line drive to right fielder Garrett Jones.   Nick Punto scores.    Matt Kemp to 2nd.
Carl Crawford grounds out, second baseman Neil Walker to first baseman Gaby Sanchez.
Mark Ellis flies out to center fielder Andrew McCutchen.
Justin Sellers homers (1) on a fly ball to left center field.
